Selepas hari ini,
kau mungkin takkan jumpa dia lagi.

739
00:43:06,890 --> 00:43:09,210
Mari kita putus.

740
00:43:14,700 --> 00:43:15,900
Semoga berjaya.

741
00:43:26,410 --> 00:43:27,380
P'James

742
00:43:28,190 --> 00:43:29,820
Dia baru saja diputuskan.

743
00:43:30,370 --> 00:43:32,170
Apa yang terjadi?

744
00:43:33,260 --> 00:43:36,110
Apa harus aku buat?
Aku tak sanggup lihat dia menangis.

745
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:38,430
Pergi hiburkan dia.

746
00:43:39,450 --> 00:43:41,160
Dia pun tak kenal aku.

747
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:43,920
Belikan saja sesuatu untuk dia.

748
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:45,480
Barangkali kau boleh buat dia tersenyum lagi.

749
00:44:07,730 --> 00:44:10,260
Ada patung lain lagi tak?

750
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:12,830
Tak ada, dah habis. Tinggal yang ini saja.

751
00:44:17,320 --> 00:44:19,860
- Aku mahu yang ini.
- 250 baht.

752
00:44:20,670 --> 00:44:22,990
Aku tak bawa tunai.
Boleh guna kad kredit?

753
00:44:23,020 --> 00:44:24,750
Aku tak tahu cara guna tu.

754
00:44:26,340 --> 00:44:28,850
Nanti aku pindah duit pada kau.

755
00:44:28,980 --> 00:44:30,340
Aku cuma terima tunai.

756
00:44:37,630 --> 00:44:39,770
Kalau begitu, aku tukar dengan ini saja.

757
00:44:39,960 --> 00:44:42,250
Oh, itu mahal sangat.

758
00:44:42,310 --> 00:44:45,420
Tak boleh, jam itu terlalu mahal.

759
00:44:50,640 --> 00:44:53,380
Oh ya, ada kertas dan pen?

760
00:44:53,630 --> 00:44:54,750
Ada.

761
00:44:55,520 --> 00:44:56,780
Nih.

762
00:45:03,060 --> 00:45:06,400
Anak, jam tangan kamu ni mahal sangat.

763
00:45:18,470 --> 00:45:19,130
Dik

764
00:45:19,490 --> 00:45:22,340
Boleh bantu berikan ini pada dia?

765
00:45:38,720 --> 00:45:40,370
Ada orang nak kasi ini untuk kau.

766
00:45:46,630 --> 00:45:49,150
(Senyum ya)

767
00:46:31,200 --> 00:46:33,120
Kenapa kau nampak bodoh begini?

768
00:46:34,280 --> 00:46:35,270
Hei North

769
00:46:36,940 --> 00:46:39,070
Jah cakap apa pada kau?

770
00:46:39,440 --> 00:46:40,780
Ohh

771
00:46:41,120 --> 00:46:43,880
- Aku baru diputuskan.
- Hah?

772
00:46:44,100 --> 00:46:45,640
- Hah?
- Kau bercinta ke tadi?

773
00:46:45,800 --> 00:46:47,420
- Hei
- Kau okay tak?

774
00:46:47,780 --> 00:46:49,510
Tak apa.

775
00:46:50,070 --> 00:46:51,300
Kau pasti kau okay?

776
00:46:52,140 --> 00:46:53,210
Baru saja diputuskan.

777
00:46:53,380 --> 00:46:54,550
Lihat sini.

778
00:46:54,640 --> 00:46:56,780
Comel kan?

779
00:46:56,820 --> 00:46:59,240
Nampak kelakar.

780
00:46:59,260 --> 00:47:00,750
- Orang lain beri kau ke?
- Ya.

781
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:02,090
Sangat comel!

782
00:47:02,150 --> 00:47:03,100
Aduh!

783
00:47:03,270 --> 00:47:04,580
Mirip kau sikit.

784
00:47:04,690 --> 00:47:05,900
Cocok untuk kau.

785
00:47:06,030 --> 00:47:09,290
- Kau kata muka aku macam itik ni?
- Tak, tak!

786
00:47:09,390 --> 00:47:11,050
- Tengoklah dia tu.
- Tapi comel lah.

787
00:47:11,120 --> 00:47:12,210
Comelnya!

788
00:47:12,310 --> 00:47:13,680
- Jomlah.
- Jumpa lagi.

789
00:47:13,720 --> 00:47:15,100
Baik.

790
00:47:44,300 --> 00:47:46,370
(Saya dah senyum. Terima kasih.)

791
00:48:12,510 --> 00:48:14,080
Kau ke mana tadi?

792
00:48:15,690 --> 00:48:17,400
Sekarang kau di mana?

793
00:48:18,480 --> 00:48:19,600
Dekat bar.

794
00:48:20,620 --> 00:48:21,930
Seorang je?

795
00:48:22,140 --> 00:48:23,030
Hmm.

796
00:48:25,230 --> 00:48:27,530
Kau kat mana? Aku datang cari.

797
00:48:52,290 --> 00:48:53,450
Kenapa?

798
00:48:54,660 --> 00:48:56,320
Kenapa minum banyak sangat?

799
00:48:57,520 --> 00:48:59,210
Aku tak tahu, Hill.

800
00:48:59,660 --> 00:49:01,000
Aku pun tak faham.

801
00:49:13,910 --> 00:49:15,650
Kenapa?

802
00:49:15,970 --> 00:49:18,160
- Kenapa?
- Hei Jo...

803
00:49:18,270 --> 00:49:19,510
Tenanglah.

804
00:49:21,030 --> 00:49:23,320
Aku tak suka rasa macam ni.

805
00:49:24,950 --> 00:49:27,480
Aku tak suka diriku yang begini.

806
00:49:28,650 --> 00:49:29,750
Hill

807
00:49:30,980 --> 00:49:33,520
Pernah tak kau jumpa seseorang
yang kau mahu temani selamanya...

808
00:49:34,110 --> 00:49:35,600
...tapi kau tak mampu?

809
00:49:38,560 --> 00:49:40,530
Kau rela beri segalanya pada dia.

810
00:49:41,480 --> 00:49:43,200
Hampir apa saja.

811
00:49:44,450 --> 00:49:46,240
Asal boleh tengok dia tersenyum.

812
00:49:48,070 --> 00:49:49,960
Tapi kenapa...

813
00:49:51,200 --> 00:49:53,460
...kenapa aku tak mampu buat dia tetap di sisiku?

814
00:50:03,520 --> 00:50:05,330
Bro

815
00:50:06,400 --> 00:50:08,320
Kalau aku cakap aku pun ada seseorang macam tu...

816
00:50:09,290 --> 00:50:11,160
Kau percaya tak?

817
00:50:29,740 --> 00:50:31,390
Easter ke?

818
00:50:34,690 --> 00:50:36,240
East itu arah matahari terbit.

819
00:50:36,770 --> 00:50:38,020
Bagus juga.

820
00:50:38,590 --> 00:50:40,480
North maksudnya arah utara.

821
00:50:40,810 --> 00:50:43,310
Ya.

822
00:50:46,350 --> 00:50:48,990
Dia nak berangkat ke Amerika kan?

823
00:50:49,740 --> 00:50:51,220
Ruginya...

824
00:50:51,550 --> 00:50:53,800
Nampaknya dia memang tak nak berhubungan lagi.

825
00:50:56,440 --> 00:50:57,600
Hmm.

826
00:50:59,250 --> 00:51:00,770
Kalau begitu, kau pula?

827
00:51:00,960 --> 00:51:03,010
Sekarang dia mungkin benci kau.

828
00:51:06,610 --> 00:51:08,170
Mungkin.

829
00:51:08,980 --> 00:51:11,070
Tak aneh kalau dia benci aku.

830
00:51:11,560 --> 00:51:13,890
Aku sendiri pun benci diri aku.

831
00:51:17,000 --> 00:51:19,820
Tuhan tak berpihak pada kita, Hill.

832
00:51:20,470 --> 00:51:21,880
Apa yang kau nak buat sekarang?

833
00:51:22,380 --> 00:51:24,030
Apa lagi yang boleh aku buat?

834
00:51:24,350 --> 00:51:25,590
Sebenarnya...

835
00:51:27,000 --> 00:51:29,140
Kau pun tunggu dia lama, kan?

836
00:51:30,580 --> 00:51:31,840
Macam mana kau mampu?

837
00:51:33,450 --> 00:51:35,620
Tak ada apa, Jo.

838
00:51:38,260 --> 00:51:40,590
Aku memang tak boleh lupakan dia.

839
00:51:41,450 --> 00:51:43,350
Aku terperangkap di situ.

840
00:51:44,280 --> 00:51:45,760
Sama saja macam kau.

841
00:51:56,340 --> 00:51:58,900
Hill

842
00:52:00,020 --> 00:52:01,610
Bila hari esok tiba...

843
00:52:04,540 --> 00:52:06,960
...bolehkah kau lupakan semua yang terjadi hari ini?

844
00:52:09,460 --> 00:52:11,330
Semuanya.

845
00:52:12,850 --> 00:52:14,960
Termasuk kata-kata aku.

846
00:52:17,020 --> 00:52:18,730
Kenapa?

847
00:52:21,640 --> 00:52:23,680
Aku cuma tak nak fikir lagi.

848
00:52:41,140 --> 00:52:42,340
Wah...

849
00:52:44,910 --> 00:52:47,190
Kenapa mereka mabuk sangat?

850
00:52:48,310 --> 00:52:51,460
Aku sangka Hill boleh jaga Jo.

851
00:52:52,640 --> 00:52:55,820
- Kenapa jadi begini?
- Aku pun tak tahu.

852
00:52:56,070 --> 00:52:57,540
Aku pergi bayar dulu.

853
00:52:57,900 --> 00:52:59,670
Hantar mereka balik rumah.

854
00:53:00,200 --> 00:53:01,280
Okey.

855
00:53:03,220 --> 00:53:04,750
Jom, jangan minum lagi.

856
00:53:05,310 --> 00:53:06,520
Hill

857
00:53:09,180 --> 00:53:12,270
Selepas hari itu,
aku lupa semua tentang Ter.

858
00:53:12,400 --> 00:53:15,060
Tapi Hill ingat semuanya.

859
00:53:16,130 --> 00:53:17,660
Akhirnya

860
00:53:18,130 --> 00:53:19,970
Aku tetap tak bisa lepaskan kau.

861
00:53:20,600 --> 00:53:22,640
Lepas itu kalian bergaduh.

862
00:53:22,800 --> 00:53:24,790
Sebab teman lelaki baru bekas kau.

863
00:53:30,960 --> 00:53:32,270
Maaf.

864
00:53:33,190 --> 00:53:35,060
Terima kasih.

865
00:53:42,040 --> 00:53:44,780
Kalau aku tahu kau bakal menangis begini...

866
00:53:45,380 --> 00:53:47,000
...aku takkan beritahu kau.

867
00:53:47,640 --> 00:53:48,990
Macam mana boleh tak menangis...

868
00:53:49,140 --> 00:53:50,440
Perkara besar macam ini.

869
00:53:51,750 --> 00:53:54,550
Lebih penting dari kisah aku,
sekarang kau menangis.

870
00:54:00,250 --> 00:54:02,740
Kenapa kau baik sangat dengan aku? Kenapa sayang sangat?

871
00:54:03,390 --> 00:54:04,910
Sudah sekian lama.

872
00:54:05,240 --> 00:54:07,280
Pasti kau amat sakit hati.

873
00:54:07,820 --> 00:54:09,920
Tapi itu tak sebanding lihat kau menangis sekarang.

874
00:54:11,500 --> 00:54:12,760
Cukuplah.

875
00:54:13,150 --> 00:54:15,000
Jangan nangis lagi.

876
00:54:18,080 --> 00:54:19,750
Baik, aku tak nangis lagi.

877
00:54:24,800 --> 00:54:26,310
Nasib baik...

878
00:54:26,760 --> 00:54:28,780
...aku tak pergi ke Amerika.

879
00:54:30,400 --> 00:54:32,220
Kalau aku ke Amerika...

880
00:54:32,750 --> 00:54:34,840
...aku tak tahu apa yang akan jadi.

881
00:54:35,020 --> 00:54:37,280
Aku cuma akan sering ke Amerika, itu saja.

882
00:54:41,930 --> 00:54:43,600
Terima kasih banyak.

883
00:54:44,610 --> 00:54:46,270
Terima kasih kerana tunggu aku begitu lama.

884
00:54:48,150 --> 00:54:50,080
Terima kasih kerana tak pernah tinggalkan aku.

885
00:54:51,410 --> 00:54:52,930
Aku cinta padamu, P'.

886
00:54:54,210 --> 00:54:55,670
Aku sangat cinta padamu.

887
00:54:57,970 --> 00:54:59,850
Aku pun cinta padamu, North.

888
00:55:14,660 --> 00:55:15,850
North

889
00:55:16,960 --> 00:55:19,130
Tak perlu panggil namaku lagi.

890
00:55:19,570 --> 00:55:21,580
Kalau bukan nama, nak panggil apa?

891
00:55:21,740 --> 00:55:22,630
Sayang, ke?

892
00:55:22,670 --> 00:55:23,610
Hei...

893
00:55:24,260 --> 00:55:26,600
- Sayang...
- Jangan.

894
00:55:30,450 --> 00:55:33,850
Sebenarnya aku pun tak pasti.

895
00:55:34,190 --> 00:55:36,950
Selalu saja aku minta sesuatu padamu.

896
00:55:37,630 --> 00:55:39,260
Sebenarnya tak begitu.

897
00:55:39,620 --> 00:55:41,560
Kau yang buat aku ingin berubah.

898
00:55:42,520 --> 00:55:43,660
Kau inspirasiku.

899
00:55:43,870 --> 00:55:45,410
Dan juga bahagiaku.

900
00:55:47,800 --> 00:55:49,350
Jangan cakap macam tu.

901
00:55:49,960 --> 00:55:51,560
Kau tak perlu buat apa-apa.

902
00:55:52,360 --> 00:55:53,960
Cukup kau di sisiku.

903
00:55:55,210 --> 00:55:57,010
Untuk selamanya, boleh?

904
00:56:00,830 --> 00:56:02,350
Aku janji.

905
00:56:02,510 --> 00:56:03,880
Aku takkan pergi ke mana-mana.

906
00:56:04,700 --> 00:56:06,750
Aku janji padamu.

907
00:56:37,150 --> 00:56:38,440
Jangan nangis lagi.

908
00:56:50,440 --> 00:56:52,410
(Iklan Minggu Depan)
Mak aku jemput kau ke rumah.

909
00:56:52,480 --> 00:56:53,830
Kita pergi rumah aku juga, nak?

910
00:56:54,840 --> 00:56:57,880
Aku ada hadiah untuk kau.

911
00:56:57,950 --> 00:56:59,890
Berikan ini pada orang yang kau cinta.

912
00:56:59,920 --> 00:57:01,220
Ini untuk kau, Ter.

913
00:57:01,320 --> 00:57:03,020
Bintang Jatuh dan Bulan

914
00:57:03,160 --> 00:57:06,840
Asalkan kau di sisiku,
aku tak peduli masa depan.

915
00:57:07,080 --> 00:57:09,600
Kejutan

